1.) if user attempts to register with an already used email address, it will not let them, but there is no alert for that. 
2.) if the user selects the current location, then enters an new address in the search bar, and then selects away from the map, 
    the application will still present the results of the current location search
3.) When a user registers for an account, after they are redirected to the homepage, they will have to refresh the page to be able 
    to see their user name on the top right
4.) Some form entrys do not have working validations associated with them
